This package directory contains the OpenWrt LuCI packaging metadata for luci-app-teamtalk.

Usage:
  - Place this directory inside an OpenWrt build root under package/luci-app-teamtalk.
  - Build with the OpenWrt build system, which will compile PO translations from po/ into LMO language packages.

Language handling:
  - `LUCIPKG_LANG:=en zh-cn` tells the build system to generate separate luci-i18n-teamtalk-en and luci-i18n-teamtalk-zh-cn packages.
  - Do not install the same translation files in both the main package and the i18n packages, or opkg will report file conflicts.

If you want to ship translations only inside the main package, remove the separate language package generation and install compiled `.lmo` files directly under usr/lib/lua/luci/i18n/.
